snippet.title: SANABI - Prologue Demo Trailer
snippet.description: This brand new trailer SANABI's story and impressive background which were first revealed in the second closed beta. Proving to be eye-catching, Mago City's business district is from Chapter 2 of the game. The trailer also shows the newly added rope ability that allows for quick movement across the map while eliminating enemies, as well as the new Monster Warrior to increase anticipation for the upcoming Early Access version.
